			+productItem('Ellery X M\'O Capsule', 'product.html', 'img/product/product-m-07-thumb.jpg', 'Known for her sculptural takes on traditional tailoring, Australian arbiter of cool Kym Ellery teams up with Moda Operandi.', '$52.00')
